In anticipation of the worldwide celebration of the month of love and particularly Valentine&rsquo;s Day, DusitD2 Nairobi hosted an elaborate event titled &lsquo;Chocolate Making Demo&rsquo;.The event was headlined by the hotel&rsquo;s new executive pastry chef, Anis Mouldi. The demo is part of the hotel&rsquo;s second Annual Chocolate Festival.The guests were shown how to make various chocolate delicacies in all shapes and sizes using ingredients like cashew nuts, raisins and berries.